        "authorId" : "357ca1f7-3359-41aa-b021-7af559dbb7f0",
        "body" : "Running the package tests after the recipe are nice but usually not really necessary.\r\n\r\nThere are two options: tell `conda build` to copy test files from the recipe (and add them to the recipe): https://docs.conda.io/projects/conda-build/en/latest/resources/define-metadata.html#test-files, or tell `conda build` to copy files from the source: https://docs.conda.io/projects/conda-build/en/latest/resources/define-metadata.html#source-files",
        "createdAt" : "2019-03-25T16:02:06Z",
        "updatedAt" : "2019-03-26T13:02:06Z",
